'''Taznatit''' tga [[Tamaziɣt|tutlayt]] z [[Tutlayin timaziɣin|tutlayin n imaziɣn]] lli sawaln [[Amaziɣ|imaziɣn]] ɣ tamazirt n [[Dzayr]]. Ar as nttini [[tamaziɣt]] n tigurarin niɣd [[tamaziɣt]] n tawat. Tg awal n tqbilin tiznatiyin niɣ znata n iffus n tamurt n [[Dzayr]]. Tutlayt ad tga yat zzɣ tutlayin n [[Dzayr]] lli ttini is tnɣuba ɣ tgira n 1985 ɣ iɣrman d iduwwarn n [[Twat]] d tsggiwin Tamntit d Tittaf.

Timyurin n igmmaḍn n tmizar ad n tmdyazt d uzawan s Taznatit ttyuran d frurin ɣ warratn n [[Mulud Mεamri]]. Tettuzemmam ɣ imṣṭirn imzwura n tusna n ufgan n [[Yunisku|-{UNESCO}-]]

